
'''''Azali''''' ni film y'ikinamico yo muri [[Gana]]  yasohotse 2018 iyobowe na Kwabena Gyansah<ref>Watch Azali | Netflix <nowiki>https://www.netflix.com</nowiki> › title</ref> . Yatoranijwe muri [[Gana]] muri Filime Nziza Mpuzamahanga igaragara mu bihembo bya 92 Awards Academy, ariko ntabwo yatowe.  Bwari ubwambere [[Gana|Ghana]] itanga firime  nziza muri Oscar award<ref name=":0">Azali – A Netflix Ghanaian Movie - AfroCentric Online <nowiki>https://afrocentriconline.ca</nowiki> › azali</ref>. 

== Umugambi ==
Umukobwa ukiri muto, Amina, abana na nyina, nyirakuru na nyirarume mu mudugudu muto hanze ya Accra<ref>AZALI | Movie Review <nowiki>https://www.talkafricanmovies.com</nowiki> › Home › AZALI</ref>. Abaho ubuzima bwiza ariko burambiranye nyina yifuza kumubohora<ref>Kwabena Gyansah's Film & Ghana's First-Ever Oscar ... <nowiki>https://www.bellanaija.com</nowiki> › kwabena-gyansah-azali</ref>. Nyirakuru yifuriza Amina kurongora umusaza ukomoka mu mudugudu wabo<ref>AZALI (FATE) - Festival International du Film black de Montréal <nowiki>https://montrealblackfilm.com</nowiki> › movie › azali-fate-2</ref>. Nyina wa Amina arigaragambya kandi agurisha Amina ku muntu atazi atizeye ka  azabona ubuzima bwiza muri uyu mujyi<ref>AZALI (FATE) - Festival International du Film black de Montréal <nowiki>https://montrealblackfilm.com</nowiki> › movie › azali-fate-2</ref>. Mu rugendo rwe Amina ahura numusore nawe wagurishijwe akiri umusore kandi muburyo bumwe, aba inshuti ye yonyine<ref name=":0" />. Bombi bahunze hamwe nitsinda rito ry'abana nabo bagurishijwe. Mugihe bombi batangiye imirimo itandukanye binyuze muri Accra bagerageza kubona ibyo bakomeza<ref>Azali - film 2019 - Orange Cinéday <nowiki>https://cineday.orange.fr</nowiki> › films › az...</ref>.

